snippet.title: Operation: Tango - Reveal Trailer | PS4
snippet.description: IT TAKES TWO to save the world in this Asymmetrical Spy Thriller. Pair up with a friend as a special agent or elite hacker, and work together to bring a high-tech global menace to its knees.
